|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Rung 1: Measure temperature                                              |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|      TempSensor_1        TempSensor_2        …         TempSensor_10      |
|      ------[ ]----------[ ]---------- … ----------[ ]----------------   |
|                        (Analog Inputs)                                  |
|      TempValue_1 = ReadTemp(I0.0)                                        |
|      TempValue_2 = ReadTemp(I0.1)                                        |
|      …                                                                   |
|      TempValue_10 = ReadTemp(I0.9)                                       |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Rung 2: Compare sensor temperature against setpoint (100°C)              |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|      TempValue_1 >= 100    TempValue_2 >= 100     …    TempValue_10 >= 100|
|      ------[ ]------------[ ]------------ … ---------[ ]---------------- |
|                              AND                                         |
|      HeaterOn = 1                                                         |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|      If all sensors are >= 100°C, the heater remains ON                  |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Rung 3: Start 2-hour timer after reaching 100°C                           |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|      AllTempSensorsAbove100 AND TimerStart (internal bit)                |
|      ------[ ]-----------------------------------------------------------|
|                            ---[ TON ]--- Timer1 (2hr)                    |
|                                                                           |
|      If all sensors >= 100°C, start the 2-hour timer. After Timer1 done,  |
|      turn OFF the heater.                                                 |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Rung 4: Stop heating after 2 hours                                        |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|      Timer1.Done (TimerDone)                                             |
|      ------[ ]-----------------------------------------------------------|
|                        ---| Heater = OFF |---                            |
|                                                                           |
|      When Timer1 completes 2 hours, turn off the heater.                  |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
